premise_source_doc_sentence: The Saxon Stories  (  also known as `` Saxon Tales '' / `` Saxon Chronicles '' in the USA and `` The Warrior Chronicles '' and since the BBC TV adaptation as `` The Last Kingdom Series '' in the UK  )  is a continuing historical novel series written by Bernard Cornwell about 9th and 10th century Britain .
